751
00:26:59,840 --> 00:27:01,440
 Poljupca mi nisi dao,

752
00:27:01,440 --> 00:27:02,940
 a ona od kako uđene

753
00:27:02,940 --> 00:27:04,360
 prestavi mi noge cjelivati.

754
00:27:04,360 --> 00:27:06,580
 Ulje mi glave nisi pomazao,

755
00:27:06,580 --> 00:27:08,700
 a ona mi pomašću noge pomazao.

756
00:27:08,700 --> 00:27:10,080
 Stoga kažem ti,

757
00:27:10,080 --> 00:27:11,760
 oprošteni su joj gresi

758
00:27:11,760 --> 00:27:15,040
 jer ljubljaše mnogo.

759
00:27:15,040 --> 00:27:17,360
 Komu se malo oprašta,

760
00:27:17,360 --> 00:27:18,040
 malo ljubi.

761
00:27:18,040 --> 00:27:19,460
 A ženi reče,

762
00:27:19,460 --> 00:27:21,200
 oprošteni su ti gresi.

763
00:27:21,200 --> 00:27:23,160
 E sad, Isus zna da su

764
00:27:23,160 --> 00:27:24,380
 oprošteni gresi.

765
00:27:24,380 --> 00:27:27,700
 Ok, oni to možda mogu znati

766
00:27:27,700 --> 00:27:29,000
 jer je Isus i sve zna.

767
00:27:29,000 --> 00:27:31,300
 Ali na njenom ponašanju

768
00:27:31,300 --> 00:27:33,220
 se moglo vidi da su oprošteni gresi.

769
00:27:33,220 --> 00:27:34,600
 Jer prodovi

770
00:27:34,600 --> 00:27:39,520
 toga da primila Božju ljubav

771
00:27:39,520 --> 00:27:40,920
 i Božje spasnje su vidljivi.

772
00:27:41,380 --> 00:27:43,340
 Ona je bila bludnica

773
00:27:43,340 --> 00:27:45,060
 koju su svi prezirali

774
00:27:45,060 --> 00:27:47,440
 i ona se našla u kući

775
00:27:47,440 --> 00:27:49,660
 među onima koji su zagorčali život.

776
00:27:49,660 --> 00:27:50,540
 Farizeji.

777
00:27:50,540 --> 00:27:52,740
 Koji su pljuvali,

778
00:27:52,740 --> 00:27:54,080
 koji su htjeli ubiti.

779
00:27:54,080 --> 00:27:55,520
 Ona se među njima našla.

780
00:27:55,520 --> 00:27:57,540
 Nije pokazivala gorčinu.

781
00:27:57,540 --> 00:27:59,280
 Nije pokazivala srđbu.

782
00:27:59,280 --> 00:28:00,780
 Nije pokazivala nemir.

783
00:28:00,780 --> 00:28:02,020
 Sve što je pokazivalo

784
00:28:02,020 --> 00:28:03,100
 bila sama ljubav,

785
00:28:03,100 --> 00:28:04,760
 velikodušnost,

786
00:28:04,760 --> 00:28:06,600
 alebastrana posudica,

787
00:28:06,600 --> 00:28:07,340
 pomasti,

788
00:28:07,340 --> 00:28:08,980
 poniznost.

789
00:28:11,000 --> 00:28:12,540
 I to je ono što mi

790
00:28:12,540 --> 00:28:13,480
 trebamo pokazati

791
00:28:13,480 --> 00:28:14,680
 koji znamo da nam je

792
00:28:14,680 --> 00:28:15,720
 gospodin oprostio.

793
00:28:15,720 --> 00:28:17,280
 To je da nas je spasio.

794
00:28:24,420 --> 00:28:27,640
 moja neka iskustva sa obraćanicima.

795
00:28:27,640 --> 00:28:30,100
 Pa većinom ko Isus.

796
00:28:30,100 --> 00:28:34,420
 Kako se zove kad bi nekog ozdravili,

797
00:28:34,420 --> 00:28:35,440
 oprostio mu grijehe,

798
00:28:35,440 --> 00:28:37,100
 na kraju što bi rekao svaki put kaže

799
00:28:37,100 --> 00:28:37,840
 ajde u miru.

800
00:28:37,840 --> 00:28:39,520
 Pusti me na miru.

801
00:28:39,520 --> 00:28:41,700
 Tako nekako ja doživljam

802
00:28:41,700 --> 00:28:43,160
 mnoge obraćanike.

803
00:28:45,760 --> 00:28:47,920
 Ali jedno posebno iskustvo

804
00:28:47,920 --> 00:28:49,040
 je bilo sa John Pridmorom.

805
00:28:49,040 --> 00:28:50,960
 Na njemu sam baš vidio

806
00:28:50,960 --> 00:28:51,940
 ovo što sam sad pričao.

807
00:28:51,940 --> 00:28:53,520
 On je bio čovjek

808
00:28:53,520 --> 00:28:54,760
 koji me je mnogo oprošteno

809
00:28:54,760 --> 00:28:55,520
 i vidilo se na njemu

810
00:28:55,520 --> 00:28:56,280
 da mnogo ljubi.

811
00:28:56,280 --> 00:28:56,780
 Ne znam,

812
00:28:56,780 --> 00:28:58,380
 vjerojatno ste svi mali prilike,

813
00:28:58,380 --> 00:28:59,640
 susre se s njim,

814
00:28:59,640 --> 00:29:00,560
 koji ste bili tad

815
00:29:00,560 --> 00:29:01,300
 ovdje u Zagrebu

816
00:29:01,300 --> 00:29:01,800
 kad je on

817
00:29:01,800 --> 00:29:02,800
 dolazio

818
00:29:02,800 --> 00:29:04,800
 i u Međugorju.

819
00:29:04,800 --> 00:29:06,480
 Ono što sam ja vidio,

820
00:29:06,480 --> 00:29:07,120
 mene je ono,

821
00:29:07,120 --> 00:29:08,120
 on me oduševio.

822
00:29:08,440 --> 00:29:08,780
 Zašto?

823
00:29:08,780 --> 00:29:10,860
 Ja sam na njemu vidio

824
00:29:10,860 --> 00:29:11,380
 da je on

825
00:29:11,380 --> 00:29:13,580
 zaista iskreno

826
00:29:13,580 --> 00:29:14,820
 zainteresiran

827
00:29:14,820 --> 00:29:15,520
 za moj život

828
00:29:15,520 --> 00:29:16,540
 kad je pričao sa mnom.

829
00:29:16,540 --> 00:29:18,260
 To se na njemu vidilo.

830
00:29:18,260 --> 00:29:19,920
 Pričaš s njim

831
00:29:19,920 --> 00:29:21,900
 i on se tebi ne nameće.

832
00:29:21,900 --> 00:29:24,280
 Ne nameće svoju priču

833
00:29:24,280 --> 00:29:24,700
 ili

834
00:29:24,700 --> 00:29:25,740
 onda te pita

835
00:29:25,740 --> 00:29:26,740
 ja pričam nešto

836
00:29:26,740 --> 00:29:27,080
 on kaže

837
00:29:27,080 --> 00:29:28,420
 i kak se ti osjećaš

838
00:29:28,420 --> 00:29:29,000
 oko toga?

839
00:29:29,000 --> 00:29:30,740
 Ja ne znam,

840
00:29:30,740 --> 00:29:31,800
 niko me nikad nije pitao

841
00:29:31,800 --> 00:29:32,660
 kak se osjećava neko

842
00:29:32,660 --> 00:29:33,460
 što sad pričao.

843
00:29:33,460 --> 00:29:35,240
 Na njemu se

844
00:29:35,240 --> 00:29:35,820
 ja sam vidio

845
00:29:35,820 --> 00:29:36,600
 da on jednako

846
00:29:36,600 --> 00:29:38,300
 razgovara sa našim fabetom

847
00:29:38,300 --> 00:29:39,980
 sa istim žarom srca

848
00:29:39,980 --> 00:29:41,260
 isto koji s Matijom.

849
00:29:41,260 --> 00:29:45,360
 Mnogo mu je oprošteno

850
00:29:45,360 --> 00:29:46,980
 i zato mnogo ljubi.

851
00:29:46,980 --> 00:29:51,860
 Zapravo

852
00:29:51,860 --> 00:29:53,100
 John je imao baš

853
00:29:53,100 --> 00:29:53,600
 jedno

854
00:29:53,600 --> 00:29:54,480
 ajmo reći

855
00:29:54,480 --> 00:29:55,580
 jače obraćenje

856
00:29:55,580 --> 00:29:56,820
 i bio je na rubu grijeha

857
00:29:56,820 --> 00:29:58,200
 i nije bio jedan od ovih

858
00:29:58,200 --> 00:30:00,820
 ko je sveta Terezija Avilska.

